'''注册表清理器'''是为[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]][[操作系统|操作系统]]设计的一类第三方[[公用程式|公用程式]]软件，其目的是在Windows[[注册表|注册表]]中删除冗余雜項。

注册表清理器的必要性是一个有争议的主題。{{citation needed|date=September 2014}}[[惡意軟件|惡意軟件]]和[[恐嚇軟件|恐嚇軟件]]通常與此類[[公用程式|公用程式]]相關聯。<ref name="Symantec">{{cite web|title=Symantec Report on Rogue Security Software|url=http://eval.symantec.com/mktginfo/enterprise/white_papers/b-symc_report_on_rogue_security_software_exec_summary_20326021.en-us.pdf|accessdate=2010-04-15|date=2009-10-28|publisher=Symantec|archive-date=2012-08-13|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/69sdVxG8b?url=http://eval.symantec.com/mktginfo/enterprise/white_papers/b-symc_report_on_rogue_security_software_exec_summary_20326021.en-us.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 优点和缺点 ==

=== 注册表损坏 ===
删除或更改某些注册表数据可能会導致系統無法啟動，或应用程序错误和崩溃。 <ref name="Symantec" />一个设计拙劣的注册表清理器可能无法确定某个键（key）是否仍被Windows使用，或者删除它可能会产生什么有害影响。这可能导致功能丧失或系统不稳定。<ref>{{cite web|title=Error: "Internet Explorer Script Error..." when scanning after running a Registry cleanup utility|url=http://service1.symantec.com/SUPPORT/sunset-c2002kb.nsf/pfdocs/2001142275577966?OpenDocument&Src=bar_sch_nam&docid=2001142275577966|accessdate=2008-05-19|date=2002-10-02|publisher=[[NortonLifeLock|Symantec]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081207155840/http://service1.symantec.com/SUPPORT/sunset-c2002kb.nsf/pfdocs/2001142275577966?OpenDocument&Src=bar_sch_nam&docid=2001142275577966|archivedate=2008-12-07|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=The .NET Framework 2.0 SP1 installation fails on a computer that has the .NET Framework 2.0 installed and that is running Windows XP, Windows Server 2003, or Windows 2000|url=http://support.microsoft.com/kb/951950|accessdate=2008-05-19|date=2008-04-24|publisher=[[Microsoft|Microsoft]]|archive-date=2015-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150215020608/http://support.microsoft.com/kb/951950|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=OL2000: Error Message: "Outlook Caused an Invalid Page Fault in Module Msvcrt.dll" When Creating an Appointment|url=http://support.microsoft.com/kb/247678|accessdate=2008-05-19|date=2003-11-05|publisher=[[Microsoft|Microsoft]]|archive-date=2014-05-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140506011023/http://support.microsoft.com/kb/247678|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 惡意軟件 ===
一些木马应用程序將註冊表清理器当作安装恶意软件的工具。<ref>{{cite press release|url=http://www.atg.wa.gov/pressrelease.aspx?&id=21026|publisher=Attorney General, [[Washington_(U.S._state)|Washington]]|date=2008-09-29|accessdate=2010-04-01|title=Fright Fight: Washington Attorney General leading battle against scareware with Microsoft|archive-date=2021-04-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210416221232/https://www.atg.wa.gov/pressrelease.aspx?&id=21026|dead-url=no}}</ref>最糟糕的是那些宣传「免费」的註冊表清理軟體被用戶發現，在产品真正的「修復」之前，必须花大量的钱购买产品。<ref>{{cite web|title=WinFixer|url=http://www.stopbadware.org/reports/reportdisplay?reportname=winfixer|accessdate=2008-06-21|publisher=StopBadware.Org|archive-date=2007-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071118122531/http://www.stopbadware.org/reports/reportdisplay?reportname=winfixer|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 清理效果 ===
在[[Windows_9x|Windows 9x]]计算机上，一个龐大的注册表可能会拖延计算机的启动时间。但是，对于基于[[Windows_NT|Windows NT]]的操作系统（包括[[Windows_XP|Windows XP]]和[[Windows_Vista|Windows Vista]]），这并不是什么问题，因为注册表的許多問題已經得到了改进。<ref>{{cite web|title=Windows 2000 Registry: Latest Features and APIs Provide the Power to Customize and Extend Your Apps|url=http://msdn.microsoft.com/msdnmag/issues/1100/Registry/|access-date=2007-07-19|archive-date=2003-04-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20030415200916/http://msdn.microsoft.com/msdnmag/issues/1100/Registry/|dead-url=no}}</ref>到目前为止，在现代版本的Windows中，由于注册表膨胀而导致的速度减慢并不是什么问题。

